<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十八年嚟都冇用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T18:21:28.000Z","msg":"終局之戰五年後，世界大致回復和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。令一邊廂，Ironman，黑寡婦同Thanos 喺地府玩緊鬥地主，過住優哉游哉嘅生活。突然，遠處傳來一陣騷亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來是 Michael Jackson 帶着佢嘅thriller 喪屍大軍，連同落咗地府嘅689同柒婆想要統治地下世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閻羅王同一眾牛頭馬面已經失守！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在絕望中主角三人決定挺身而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但由於地府缺乏武器，Ironman 情急之下只好報夢比pepper 叫佢燒件紙紮裝甲落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thanos 則馬上趕造紙紮手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幸好的是黑寡婦本來就係佈景板所以影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟他們能否成功再一次阻止災難降臨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c0a63ecc7ee0c7b409416313e41f13e9094614","tid":1128324,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35341d300aa7e515d72579d9abc701fe87892214","tid":1128324,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b261aeb9fee65500a59df359c76f43ca86e4f4f","tid":1128324,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109557f08a2e154ff448bf19b3c6e5ce0a02c85a","tid":1128324,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"😊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"啞架你？陰公<img s